1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,018
Excuse me.

2
00:00:02,018 --> 00:00:04,688
Oh, I'm sorry. I.

3
00:00:04,688 --> 00:00:06,339
I. Oh, it's. Okay.

4
00:00:06,339 --> 00:00:08,858
I didn't mean to scare you.

5
00:00:08,858 --> 00:00:13,813
I'm kind of lost.

6
00:00:13,897 --> 00:00:18,201
Lost?

7
00:00:18,268 --> 00:00:19,319
Yeah.

8
00:00:19,319 --> 00:00:21,755
I'm looking for Silent Hill.

9
00:00:21,755 --> 00:00:24,390
Is this the right way?

10
00:00:24,390 --> 00:00:25,809
Yeah.

11
00:00:25,809 --> 00:00:29,529
It's hard to see with this fog,
but there's only the one road.

12
00:00:29,763 --> 00:00:31,831
You can't miss it.

13
00:00:31,831 --> 00:00:34,200
Thanks,

14
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:36,719
but yes.

15
00:00:36,719 --> 00:00:41,808
I think you'd better stay away.

16
00:00:41,891 --> 00:00:44,878
This.

17
00:00:45,028 --> 00:00:46,629
This town.

18
00:00:46,629 --> 00:00:49,816
There's something wrong with it.

19
00:00:49,899 --> 00:00:52,051
It's kind of hard to explain, but.

20
00:00:52,051 --> 00:00:54,387
Is it dangerous?

21
00:00:54,387 --> 00:00:56,322
Maybe.

22
00:00:56,322 --> 00:00:59,509
And it's not just a fog either.

23
00:00:59,592 --> 00:01:01,477
Okay, I got it.

24
00:01:01,477 --> 00:01:03,463
I'll be careful.

25
00:01:03,463 --> 00:01:05,098
I'm not lying.

26
00:01:05,098 --> 00:01:07,901
No, I believe you.

27
00:01:07,901 --> 00:01:09,636
It's just.

28
00:01:09,636 --> 00:01:13,306
I guess I really don't care
if it's dangerous or not.

29
00:01:13,389 --> 00:01:17,143
I'm going to town either way.

30
00:01:17,226 --> 00:01:20,496
But why?

31
00:01:20,580 --> 00:01:25,101
I'm looking for someone.

32
00:01:25,168 --> 00:01:26,803
Who is it?

33
00:01:26,803 --> 00:01:29,539
Someone

34
00:01:29,622 --> 00:01:32,041
very important to me.

35
00:01:32,041 --> 00:01:35,445
I'd do anything
if I could be with her again.

